#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:77
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Instellingen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:151
msgid "Discard"
msgstr "Verwerpen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:152
msgid "Save changes"
msgstr "Wijzigingen opslaan"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:159
msgid "Passwordless sign-in via magic link or 6-character code. Configure how it looks, how it behaves, and how it recovers from edge cases. All on one page."
msgstr "Wachtwoordloos inloggen via een magische link of een 6-tekens code. Stel in hoe het eruitziet, hoe het zich gedraagt en hoe het herstelt bij randgevallen. Allemaal op één pagina."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:179
msgid "General"
msgstr "Algemeen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:180
msgid "How long links live and where users land afterwards."
msgstr "Hoe lang links geldig blijven en waar gebruikers daarna terechtkomen."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:195
msgid "Branding"
msgstr "Branding"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:196
msgid "How the sign-in card looks. Settings render on the branded login screen and in transactional emails."
msgstr "Hoe de inlogkaart eruitziet. Deze instellingen verschijnen op het gebrande inlogscherm en in transactionele e-mails."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:214
msgid "Agency credit"
msgstr "Bureaucredit"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:215
msgid "Optional \"Built by [Brand]\" line below the sign-in card. Renders only when name, URL, and favicon are all filled."
msgstr "Optionele regel \"Gemaakt door [Merk]\" onder de inlogkaart. Verschijnt alleen als naam, URL en favicon allemaal zijn ingevuld."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:231
msgid "Security &amp; throttling"
msgstr "Beveiliging &amp; throttling"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:232
msgid "Recovery layers and rate-limit caps. The \"Sign in with password\" link is the unconditional safety net. Disable it only after site-wide password auth is already off."
msgstr "Herstellagen en rate-limietplafonds. De link \"Inloggen met wachtwoord\" is het onvoorwaardelijke vangnet. Schakel deze pas uit nadat wachtwoordauthenticatie sitebreed al is uitgeschakeld."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:250
msgid "Diagnostics &amp; recovery"
msgstr "Diagnose &amp; herstel"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:251
msgid "One-shot tools for debugging and unsticking the plugin. Destructive actions ask for confirmation."
msgstr "Eenmalige hulpmiddelen om te debuggen en de plug-in weer vlot te trekken. Destructieve acties vragen om bevestiging."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:259
msgid "Send test email"
msgstr "Test-e-mail versturen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:260
msgid "One-shot diagnostic. No tokens are issued. Forces the default brand color to verify rendering."
msgstr "Eenmalige diagnose. Er worden geen tokens uitgegeven. Forceert de standaard merkkleur om de weergave te controleren."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:263
msgid "Send to my account"
msgstr "Naar mijn account sturen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:269
msgid "Revoke all magic-links and codes"
msgstr "Alle magische links en codes intrekken"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:270
msgid "Marks every unconsumed token consumed site-wide. Already-active sessions are not signed out."
msgstr "Markeert elk niet-gebruikt token sitebreed als gebruikt. Reeds actieve sessies worden niet uitgelogd."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:273
msgid "Revoke now"
msgstr "Nu intrekken"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:279
msgid "Reset throttle counters"
msgstr "Throttle-tellers resetten"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:280
msgid "Deletes every magicauth_throttle_* transient. Object-cache safe."
msgstr "Verwijdert elke magicauth_throttle_*-transient. Veilig voor object-cache."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:283
msgid "Reset now"
msgstr "Nu resetten"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:342
msgid "Branded login is enabled, but your WordPress salts are still weak. Magic links each carry their own random secret so they stay safe; your session cookies and the 6-character codes are better protected once you fix the salts. See the weak-salt notice for how."
msgstr "Het gebrande inlogscherm staat aan, maar je WordPress-salts zijn nog steeds zwak. Elke magische link draagt zijn eigen willekeurige geheim, dus die blijven veilig; je sessiecookies en de 6-tekens codes zijn beter beschermd zodra je de salts herstelt. Zie de melding over zwakke salts voor hoe."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:355
msgid "Sender address: that value had no usable characters, so it was reset to \"login\"."
msgstr "Afzenderadres: die waarde bevatte geen bruikbare tekens en is teruggezet op \"login\"."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:430
msgid "Logo: selected attachment is not an image."
msgstr "Logo: het geselecteerde bestand is geen afbeelding."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:446
msgid "Logo: SVG contains active content (script / event handlers / javascript:). Re-export without scripting."
msgstr "Logo: SVG bevat actieve inhoud (script / event-handlers / javascript:). Exporteer opnieuw zonder scripting."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:454
msgid "Logo: only PNG, JPG, WebP, or SVG are allowed."
msgstr "Logo: alleen PNG, JPG, WebP of SVG zijn toegestaan."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:464
msgid "Logo: file content does not match a supported image format."
msgstr "Logo: de bestandsinhoud komt niet overeen met een ondersteund afbeeldingsformaat."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:479
msgid "Link &amp; code lifetime"
msgstr "Levensduur van link &amp; code"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:480
msgid "Both the magic link and the typeable code share one expiry. Range 1–30 minutes."
msgstr "De magische link en de typbare code delen één vervaltijd. Bereik 1–30 minuten."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:484
msgid "minutes"
msgstr "minuten"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:496
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:500
msgid "Max link uses"
msgstr "Max. linkgebruik"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:497
msgid "2 absorbs URL-scanner prefetch plus the user's click. Set to 1 for strict single-use."
msgstr "2 vangt prefetch door URL-scanners op plus de klik van de gebruiker. Stel in op 1 voor strikt eenmalig gebruik."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:517
msgid "Auto (admin or home, by capability)"
msgstr "Automatisch (beheer of home, op basis van rechten)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:518
msgid "Site home"
msgstr "Sitehome"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:519
msgid "Admin dashboard"
msgstr "Beheerdashboard"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:524
msgid "Default redirect after sign-in"
msgstr "Standaard doorverwijzing na inloggen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:525
msgid "Where users land when no specific destination was requested."
msgstr "Waar gebruikers terechtkomen als er geen specifieke bestemming is opgevraagd."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:549
msgid "Replace WordPress login screen"
msgstr "WordPress-inlogscherm vervangen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:551
msgid "Why is this flagged?"
msgstr "Waarom is dit gemarkeerd?"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:551
msgid "Heads up: weak salts"
msgstr "Let op: zwakke salts"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:551
msgid "You can turn this on now, but the salts in"
msgstr "Je kunt dit nu inschakelen, maar de salts in"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:551
msgid "are weak — fixing them first is recommended."
msgstr "zijn zwak — het wordt aanbevolen die eerst te herstellen."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:551
msgid "How to fix →"
msgstr "Hoe te herstellen →"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:554
msgid "Intercepts wp-login.php and serves the branded MagicAuth screen. The native form stays available at ?magicauth=off as a recovery path."
msgstr "Onderschept wp-login.php en toont het gebrande MagicAuth-scherm. Het oorspronkelijke formulier blijft beschikbaar via ?magicauth=off als herstelpad."

#. translators: "language switcher" is WordPress's own locale selector on the login screen.
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:576
msgid "Hide language switcher"
msgstr "Taalwisselaar verbergen"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:579
msgid "WordPress adds a language selector to the login screen when extra languages are installed. MagicAuth places it under the card. Turn this on to hide it on the branded screen; the recovery login at ?magicauth=off keeps it."
msgstr "WordPress voegt een taalkeuze toe aan het inlogscherm wanneer er extra talen zijn geïnstalleerd. MagicAuth plaatst die onder de kaart. Schakel dit in om de taalkeuze op het gebrande scherm te verbergen; de herstel-login op ?magicauth=off behoudt die."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:598
msgid "Company name"
msgstr "Bedrijfsnaam"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:599
msgid "Your short business name. No taglines, slogans, or separators."
msgstr "Je korte bedrijfsnaam. Geen taglines, slogans of scheidingstekens."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:616
msgid "Sender email address"
msgstr "Afzender-e-mailadres"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:617
msgid "The address sign-in emails are sent from. Only the part before the @ is editable — it stays on your own domain so messages pass spam checks (SPF/DKIM/DMARC) instead of being flagged as forged. Letters, digits, and . _ - + only."
msgstr "Het adres waarvandaan inlogmails worden verstuurd. Alleen het deel vóór de @ is bewerkbaar — het blijft op je eigen domein, zodat berichten de spamcontroles (SPF/DKIM/DMARC) doorstaan in plaats van als vervalst te worden gemarkeerd. Alleen letters, cijfers en . _ - +."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:631
msgid "Logo"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:632
msgid "PNG, JPG, or WebP. Existing SVG attachments may also be selected. Capped at 48px height on the sign-in card."
msgstr "PNG, JPG of WebP. Bestaande SVG-bijlagen kunnen ook worden geselecteerd. Beperkt tot 48px hoogte op de inlogkaart."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:643
msgid "Brand color"
msgstr "Merkkleur"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:645
msgid "Auto-derives readable button text via YIQ luminance. Current contrast:"
msgstr "Leidt automatisch leesbare knoptekst af via YIQ-luminantie. Huidig contrast:"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:651
msgid "Color picker"
msgstr "Kleurkiezer"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:665
msgid "Brand name"
msgstr "Merknaam"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:666
msgid "Shown bold in the credit line."
msgstr "Vetgedrukt weergegeven in de creditregel."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:669
msgid "Acme Studio"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:681
msgid "Brand URL"
msgstr "Merk-URL"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:682
msgid "Opens in a new tab. Must start with http:// or https://."
msgstr "Opent in een nieuw tabblad. Moet beginnen met http:// of https://."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:695
msgid "Brand favicon"
msgstr "Merk-favicon"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:696
msgid "Square 32×32 or larger. PNG, JPG, WebP, or SVG."
msgstr "Vierkant 32×32 of groter. PNG, JPG, WebP of SVG."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:706
msgid "Credit label"
msgstr "Creditlabel"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:707
msgid "Text shown before the brand name. Leave blank for the default (\"Built by\")."
msgstr "Tekst die vóór de merknaam wordt getoond. Laat leeg voor de standaard (\"Gemaakt door\")."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:710
msgid "Built by"
msgstr "Gemaakt door"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:722
msgid "\"Sign in with password\" link"
msgstr "Link \"Inloggen met wachtwoord\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:723
msgid "Always-visible recovery link on every form. Only disable this if you have already disabled WordPress password authentication site-wide."
msgstr "Altijd zichtbare herstellink op elk formulier. Schakel dit alleen uit als je WordPress-wachtwoordauthenticatie al sitebreed hebt uitgeschakeld."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:740
msgid "Per-IP window (hours)"
msgstr "Venster per IP (uren)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:741
msgid "Per-IP max requests"
msgstr "Max. verzoeken per IP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:742
msgid "Per-IP code window (hours)"
msgstr "Codevenster per IP (uren)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:743
msgid "Per-IP max code attempts"
msgstr "Max. codepogingen per IP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:748
msgid "Per-email cooldown"
msgstr "Afkoeltijd per e-mail"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:749
msgid "Seconds between consecutive link requests for the same email. 0 disables. Default 60. Replaced the per-email hard cap in v1.3.7. That cap was a DoS primitive any IP could weaponize against any victim email."
msgstr "Seconden tussen opeenvolgende linkverzoeken voor hetzelfde e-mailadres. 0 schakelt het uit. Standaard 60. Verving de harde limiet per e-mail in v1.3.7. Die limiet was een DoS-primitief dat elk IP tegen elk slachtoffer-e-mailadres kon inzetten."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:753
msgid "seconds"
msgstr "seconden"

